<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.6.6">
<l>tārittu nūṟṟuvar tantaicoṟ koḷḷātu</l>
<l>pōruyttu vantu pukuntavar maṇṇāḷap</l>
<l>pāritta maṉṉar paṭappañ cavarkkuvaṉṟu</l>
<l>tēruytta kaikaḷāl cappāṇi tēvaki ciṅkamē cappāṇi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With the hands that led the chariot of the five long ago</l>
<l>so that the king who had prepared to rule the earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">—he who, not accepting the word of the father of the hundred,</l>
<l rend="indent">came to conduct battle—</l>
<l>perished, [clap] cappāṇi!</l>
<l>Lion of Devakī, [clap] cappāṇi!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
